Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/structured-world/coordinode

Package: coordinode
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, systemd, adduser
Description: Unified database for AI-native applications
 CoordiNode is a unified database combining graph, vector, full-text,
 document and time-series modalities in one engine. Queries use OpenCypher;
 writes commit atomically across modalities.
